{
  "text": "Filtration matrix Another importance aspect is the filtration matrix that defines the distance in persistent homology analysis. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] We denote the Euclidean distance between atom i at (x i , y i , z i ) and atom j at (x j , y j , z j ) to be",
